ord Effectiveness and Sales Impact\"", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training - 10 Most Powerful Words.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Mastering the 10 Power Words for Sales Excellence\"", "\"Sales Training - 12 Ways to Be Top Salesperson.docx\" → SOPs, Training, Tasks", "Generating SOPs from \"Sales Training - 12 Ways to Be Top Salesperson.docx\"...", "Built SOP: \"Customer Approach and Engagement Process\"", "Built SOP: \"Inventory Management and Alternative Solutions\"", "Built SOP: \"Sales Completion and Customer Follow-Up\"", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training - 12 Ways to Be Top Salesperson.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Mastering the 12 Principles of Exceptional Sales Performance\"", "Generating task lists from \"Sales Training - 12 Ways to Be Top Salesperson.docx\"...", "Built task list: \"Daily Sales Excellence Checklist\"", "Built task list: \"Advanced Sales Performance Checklist\"", "\"Sales Training - Greeting & Building Rapport.docx\" → SOPs, Training", "Generating SOPs from \"Sales Training - Greeting & Building Rapport.docx\"...", "Built SOP: \"Customer Greeting Protocol - Stop and Drop in 15\"", "Built SOP: \"Training New Associates on Customer Greeting Standards\"", "Built SOP: \"Monitoring Customer Service Standards and First Impressions\"", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training - Greeting & Building Rapport.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Creating Memorable First Impressions: The Stop and Drop in 15 Rule\"", "\"Sales Training - Customer Service Facts.docx\" → Training, Knowledge Base", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training - Customer Service Facts.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"The Power of Customer Service: Understanding the Impact\"", "Generating knowledge base articles from \"Sales Training - Customer Service Facts.docx\"...", "Built KB article: \"Customer Retention Statistics and Cost Impact\"", "Built KB article: \"Complaint Resolution and Recovery Statistics\"", "\"Sales Training - How to Add-On to Any Sale.docx\" → SOPs, Training", "Generating SOPs from \"Sales Training - How to Add-On to Any Sale.docx\"...", "Built SOP: \"Add-On Selling Using Picture-Perfect Techniques\"", "Built SOP: \"The Cake Analogy Enhancement Technique\"", "Built SOP: \"Prevention-Based Add-On Selling Strategy\"", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training - How to Add-On to Any Sale.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Mastering Add-On Sales Through Visual Storytelling\"", "\"Tips for Improving Language on the Sales Floor.docx\" → SOPs, Training", "Generating SOPs from \"Tips for Improving Language on the Sales Floor.docx\"...", "Built SOP: \"Customer Communication and Language Best Practices\"", "Built SOP: \"Handling Customer Concerns and Policy Exceptions\"", "Built SOP: \"Product Availability and Alternative Solutions\"", "Generating training modules from \"Tips for Improving Language on the Sales Floor.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Elevating Your Sales Floor Language\"", "\"Sales Training Manual.docx\" → SOPs, Training", "Generating SOPs from \"Sales Training Manual.docx\"...", "Built SOP: \"Customer Greeting and Initial Engagement\"", "Built SOP: \"Dressing Room Sales Maximization\"", "Built SOP: \"Complete Customer Experience and Follow-Up\"", "Generating training modules from \"Sales Training Manual.docx\"...", "Built training module: \"Building Customer Connections: The Art of Authentic Selling\"", "\"Body Types.pdf\" → Training, Knowledge Base", "Generating training modules from \"Body Types.pdf\"...", "Server restarted during generation — please click Generate again to retry."]', '46870047', '2026-04-14 18:56:37.727934', '2026-04-14 19:06:47.847604');


