	('7f95a1f3-58e6-4e41-85c5-d065a4f11a06', 'b0396051-34a1-475b-addc-771e580a5224', 'ai_item', '13bd4e49-8135-4102-bb6d-15f032a2c923', 'Customer Loyalty Program Enrollment at Checkout | Role: Lead | Complete process for identifying existing customers and enrolling new customers in the loyalty program during checkout to maximize customer retention and data collection. | Initial Checkout Greeting | Start with ''Hi! Did you find everything you needed today?'' Wait for customer response and respond accordingly to any needs or concerns. | Check Customer Status | Ask ''Have you ever shopped with us before?'' to determine if customer is in the system. | Decision: Customer Account Status | Determine next steps based on customer''s shopping history | Loyalty Program Enrollment Pitch | Use script: ''Would you like to join our Customer Loyalty Program? It''s not like a credit card. It''s just a FREE rewards and perks program! You earn money back on your purchases, you''re the first to know about new arrivals, sales, and promotions, and you get a birthday discount during your birthday month! It only takes about 2 minutes to get signed up. Are you interested in joining today?'' | Decision: Enrollment Response | Handle customer''s decision about joining loyalty program | Complete Transaction | Inform customer of any current promotions and attach flyer to receipt or put in bag with receipt.', '96129ae8890b33b6', '[-0.081523344,0.023752354,0.0016414272,-0.014004358,0.011912078,0.028176965,0.028112726,0.009819443,-0.0023094087,-0.0525699,0.06432298,0.035671063,0.0044071716,-0.08330159,0.06713992,-0.043780208,0.04681074,-0.06178903,-0.0036477346,-0.024332622,-0.12407625,-0.08687389,-0.041646983,0.050495468,0.005433041,-0.00039257298,0.02793826,0.037277926,-0.032068532,0.033404972,0.015885038,0.069326155,0.10853139,0.0048686415,0.031664826,0.006548935,0.011158926,-0.03369272,-0.062277146,-0.06527549,-0.024811834,-0.065236315,-0.05811615,0.104611665,0.081422545,-0.054485336,-0.06193171,0