	('0fd4d670-256a-4cb7-aa03-48b01122b1e2', 'b0396051-34a1-475b-addc-771e580a5224', 'ai_item', 'c4758366-1bff-4431-a789-f125574107dc', 'Customer Engagement and Needs Assessment Process | Role: New Associate | A comprehensive approach to greeting customers, building rapport, and understanding their needs to provide exceptional personalized service. | Warm Greeting and Relationship Building | Greet every customer within 30 seconds of entering with a genuine smile and welcoming phrase like ''Good morning! Welcome to Our Store.'' Follow with appropriate small talk about the weather, compliment their style, or mention current trends to create a comfortable atmosphere. | Listen and Assess Customer Needs | Ask open-ended questions such as ''What brings you in today?'' or ''What kind of occasion are you shopping for?'' Give customers 70% of the talking time while you actively listen to understand their specific requirements, preferences, and budget. | Decision: Customer Response Type | Determine next steps based on how clearly the customer expresses their needs | Present Solutions Focused on Customer Value | Show items that meet their stated needs while explaining specific benefits and value. Highlight what makes each piece special, how it fits their lifestyle, and why Our Store''s selection stands out from competitors.', '5fd3aae004c35da0', '[-0.06437474,0.06808721,0.056698676,0.04459085,-0.009722469,-0.024075381,0.07822184,0.014960922,-0.019182945,-0.06556922,-0.012650005,-0.037508197,-0.04601681,0.0057290806,0.1149633,0.0071341344,0.033946346,-0.043439582,-0.010818948,0.041919533,-0.038656563,0.0071263025,0.02430059,0.049741663,-0.103964984,-0.019273488,0.047200516,0.027798722,0.017418591,-0.020034133,-0.001940068,0.10649129,0.12016301,0.007922136,-0.027729282,0.058249094,0.053416006,0.00019886708,-0.01034527,-0.019581154,-0.03605364,-0.09159438,-0.019086141,0.024086146,0.06800057,-0.118537255,0.036012877,-0.009788472,0.025246816,0.06309351,-0.059150662,-0.040896274,-0.006