	('94b4253e-9545-46b1-bb9b-3acbab9f6761', 'b0396051-34a1-475b-addc-771e580a5224', 'ai_item', '1faf40c9-7f64-4a0d-ac67-2a16411dbda9', 'Analyzing Power Word Effectiveness and Sales Impact | Role: Manager | A systematic approach for managers to measure the effectiveness of power word implementation and its impact on store sales performance and customer satisfaction. | Establish baseline metrics before implementation | Record current sales metrics including average transaction value, conversion rate, and customer satisfaction scores before implementing power word training. This will serve as your comparison benchmark. | Create tracking system for power word usage | Develop a simple tracking method to monitor which associates are consistently using power words and in what contexts. Use weekly observation sheets or customer feedback to gather this data. | Monitor sales performance indicators | Track key metrics weekly including sales per associate, average transaction value, conversion rates, and return rates. Compare these metrics to your established baseline to measure improvement. | Decision: Evaluate effectiveness and adjust strategy | Assess results after 4-6 weeks of implementation | Report results and plan next steps | Compile monthly reports showing the impact of power word implementation on sales and customer satisfaction. Share successful examples with the team and identify top performers to mentor others. Plan ongoing training sessions to maintain momentum.', '5132ead4edc76f65', '[-0.0103334645,0.047371894,-0.0570488,0.040487204,-0.07060843,0.0055868845,-0.004232424,0.036604773,-0.0030599434,-0.012888093,0.010482892,0.050445676,0.049147867,-0.013327451,0.07051969,0.036038492,0.096449785,0.050637662,-0.0512808,-0.022567362,0.06505592,0.025498966,0.064053506,0.02330201,0.038588535,0.016746257,-0.14749275,0.023545938,0.0038114553,0.050115686,-0.05127565,0.008247902,0.064608976,0.04903239,-0.033198897,-0.0069065657,0.05103945,0.04833539,0.06451511,-0.03231695,-0.07