	('00fe1f18-29b6-4c9d-9b91-64e0686120d6', 'b0396051-34a1-475b-addc-771e580a5224', 'ai_item', '637386c3-0e9c-4ce5-95c4-e155c2949297', 'Sales Completion and Customer Follow-Up | Role: Manager | A systematic approach to maximizing sales through add-on suggestions, proper checkout procedures, and post-sale customer appreciation to build long-term relationships. | Present Additional Products | At the close of the primary sale, present complementary products and accessories that enhance the customer''s purchase. Focus on items that complete the look or add versatility to their selection. | Provide Product Knowledge | Share comprehensive information about the merchandise including price points, construction details, care instructions, and how it compares to other brands. Demonstrate your expertise to build customer confidence. | Complete Transaction with Personal Touch | Process the sale efficiently while maintaining personal connection. Thank the customer by name during the transaction and ensure they have all necessary information about their purchase including care instructions and return policy. | Decision: Follow-Up Method | Determine the appropriate follow-up method based on the sale value and customer relationship potential. | Send Thank You Note | For appropriate sales, send a brief, personalized thank you note the day after the purchase. Include the customer''s name, reference their specific purchase, and express appreciation for their business. This reinforces the personal shopping experience.', '98ff7ed19d3d7464', '[-0.06324849,0.017487163,0.047355354,-0.023267081,-0.07275766,0.034172796,0.059368603,0.08272209,-0.018182477,-0.070864424,0.11082673,0.05857073,-0.023208274,-0.05713224,0.06598931,-0.040062718,0.09537931,-0.034861363,-0.041807804,-0.025766822,-0.03873498,-0.018122636,0.0332286,0.024440715,-0.062765144,-0.02487857,-0.051610123,-0.0075277584,-0.020497829,0.002914138,0.0019437425,0.056215975,0.07063342,-0.01954359,-0.052376032,0.009535036,-0.027432812,-