Greet every guest within 20 seconds of entering the store at either entrance.

"Hey, how are you today?" Respond with a helpful/inspiring question. For instance, "Are you shopping for an event in particular?" or "We have some great pieces that would look great on you, would it be alright for me to pull a few down and set up a dressing room for you?"

Free People Area

"Did you know that we''re a Free People Shop-in-Shop?"

