	('10628726-6915-47a5-a774-d8bcad26f17b', 'b0396051-34a1-475b-addc-771e580a5224', 'knowledge_doc', '43ab573c-ea3b-4aed-8499-7b1e2e0e7750:chunk:2', '[Sales Training Manual.docx] on’t let it be a bad one.  

Every day we have customers entering the store, and studies show that customers form an impression (good or bad) of the store in as little as 20 seconds.  Therefore, in Libby Story stores, we focus on the “Stop and Drop in 15” Rule.  Think of it like your childhood fire drill, “Stop, Drop, and Roll,” but its “Stop and Drop in 15!”

This simple rule defines how you should act in those first few crucial seconds. Let’s look:

Take action within 15 feet or 15 seconds.  This is whenever you see a customer enter the store, or your section, then complete steps one and two within 15 seconds.  The same goes whenever a customer comes within 15 feet of you while browsing. 

Step One: Break the ice and let the customer know that you know they are in the store.  The best way to do this is by STOPPING what you are doing, making eye contact, and giving a big smile.  These simple acts will go a long way to making the customer feel at ease and help them be open to your appr', 'fafd7d94f22bf116', '[-0.018731346,0.010938085,0.08879685,-0.03367465,0.05777049,0.037667956,0.008080636,0.010478091,0.008023956,-0.06478346,0.09498701,0.03381638,-0.024361974,0.05034128,-0.019872868,-0.03400399,0.051123083,0.025438858,-0.07180939,0.0041508917,0.08608992,-0.084155284,0.005932229,0.026493438,-0.10873541,-0.011700169,-0.029643033,-0.09073123,-0.017301386,-0.06468049,-0.004973742,0.009592561,0.12451729,-0.013498471,-0.010159231,0.011761464,0.0067768586,-0.035332438,0.082769305,-0.014421061,0.0013705009,-0.06161394,-0.102569796,0.06862123,0.059627786,-0.011289363,0.06420626,0.066369265,0.04786898,0.06427177,-0.076163284,0.04689973,0.018189196,-0.0014517228,-0.022501951,0.035122443,-0.0038334406,0.00069056125,0.02004403,-0.00053955364,0.027437076,-0.082405165,-0.041595377,-0.0019204014,-0.036337007,0.033808634,0.007169649,-0.06217408,-0.025153743,0.04449866,-0.055585865,0.010890431,-0.02395104,0.041629683,-0.03173484,0.0041625467,0.03973755,-0.081988625,0.050519735,0.012588409,-0.020056427,-0.04629048,0.026264966,0.032191835,-0.05779819,-0.07257715,0.09614982,0.00545865,-0.007983561,-0.02559397,-0.023281725,0.0048179254,-0.09413508,-0.0064662495,-0.04957451,0.0035466116,-0.07231489,0.03932317,-0.025838535,0.019346781,0.01103827,0.04836936,0.012439497,-0.07398054,-0.02123197,-0.15908323,0.05042947,0.050002187,-0.046846718,0.03211299,-0.021915749,0.022636311,0.03131834,-0.0385317,0.049606085,0.11650693,-0.016663263,0.0367655,-0.009275868,0.025827695,0.085365504,0.0959892,0.03604741,-0.027867002,-0.040010586,0.025580402,0.07020654,3.987826e-33,-0.07524092,-0.009085318,-0.07186476,0.00822625,0.039906114,-0.048814725,0.019426528,0.043894913,-0.0090641,0.084304675